    campusDetailed: 'Multi-campus, urban set-up across Bengaluru rather than a single large green campus - departments are spread across several city locations, giving a more metropolitan, dispersed college experience. Wi-Fi-enabled campuses with classrooms, computer labs and libraries geared toward both on-campus and online-degree delivery models. Strong collaborations with international and national institutions supporting research, exchange and industry linkups. Offers both full-time on-campus and Jain Online distance-learning pathways for BBA, B.Com, MBA, MCA and more, widening access for different learner profiles. Recognised by AIU, Association of Commonwealth Universities (ACU) and NIBES, supporting international academic mobility.',
