    coursesFeesDetailed: 'Programme: BBA with specialisations including Finance and Entrepreneurship - 3-year full-time. Total BBA fee (2026-27): approximately INR 4.55-7.1 Lakh depending on specialisation (tuition component ≈ INR 4.5-7.05 Lakh) - an increase of roughly 10% over the previous year. Per-year payable amount: roughly INR 1.52-2.37 Lakh. Hostel fees: approximately INR 1.05 Lakh per year (SJU hostel). NRI-category BBA fees: approximately INR 6.95-9.2 Lakh for the full course. Application fee is modest - reported at under INR 500 for the BBA programme. Scholarships are available based on academic performance in qualifying exams, family income, and category, applicable to both UG and PG programmes.',
