    campusDetailed: 'Located in Kengeri, Bangalore. Facilities include library with extensive collection, computer labs with latest software, separate hostel for boys and girls, cafeteria serving hygienic food, sports facilities, and Wi-Fi enabled campus. Small campus known for focused learning environment and personal attention to students. Off-campus hostels available near campus. Easy access from major parts of Bangalore via public transport.',
