    coursesFeesDetailed: 'PGPM + MBA (2-yr full-time, dual certification). Total tuition fee: ₹7.78 Lakhs (₹1,87,200 per semester for Sem 1-2, ₹2,01,800 per semester for Sem 3-4). Refundable academic security deposit: ₹15,000. Specializations: Finance, Marketing, HR, Digital Marketing, Operations & Supply Chain Management, Business Intelligence & Data Analytics, International Business, Entrepreneurship. BBA + GPBA (3 years): ₹4.82 Lakhs total. Scholarships up to 100% based on academic merit. Programme designed with corporate interactions, live projects, and study abroad opportunities.',
