    campusDetailed: 'Located in Koramangala, Bangalore — the city\'s startup and tech hub — on a modern campus with excellent infrastructure. Facilities include Wi-Fi-enabled campus, spacious air-conditioned smart classrooms, state-of-the-art computer labs, well-stocked library with digital resources, cafeteria serving hygienic food, recreation and sports centre. Study Abroad Programme for international exposure at partner universities. Regular guest lectures and interactive sessions with CEOs and industry leaders. Close proximity to major tech parks and corporate offices in Koramangala, Electronic City, and Whitefield.',
